                <note rend="inline" type="source">868.51 Struma Valley/7: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Greece</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Skinner</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-04-20T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 20, 1928—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>21. Referring to your 24, April 18, 5 p.m. You are expected by the Department to
                    render appropriate assistance to all responsible American companies. If you are
                    not certain about the American character of the Foundation Company (Foreign),
                    you will please report your reasons, and the Department will take into
                    consideration the sending of new instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
